snippet.title: Longplay of Elmo's Letter Adventure
snippet.description:
Longplay of Elmo's Letter Adventure, played as the NTSC version on the Nintendo 64. This game's version was released on Nov. 15th, 1999. Tell us what you think by leaving a comment down below!

00:00 - Start
00:51 - Grover's Adventure
07:34 - Big Bird's Adventure
12:52 - Ernie's Adventure
18:57 - Credits
